1
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:24,500
"Love After Addiction"

2
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:26,600
(Episode 6)

3
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,560
Next, who wants to perform?

4
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,959
If no one speaks up,
I'll just pick someone.

5
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,960
I'll do it.

6
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,120
Give me your harmonica.

7
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,400
Here.

8
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,319
My name is Yoki.

9
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,159
I...

10
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,400
It's complicated.

11
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:18,959
His skill is just so-so.

12
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,840
Yeah, right, Brother Yang?

13
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,600
I want a turn too!

14
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,160
It's raining!

15
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:13,039
Go home and take in the laundry!

16
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,375
The clothes are all getting soaked.

17
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:14,800
Hurry up!
No, no...

18
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:16,439
Hurry up! Hurry up!

19
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,720
Go dance at home by yourself.

20
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:31,360
Really?

21
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,680
Why did you leave without saying anything?

22
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:03,560
Weren't there so many people

23
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,920
crowding around you this morning?

24
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:09,279
You got even hotter!

25
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,519
No, I...

26
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:14,519
I... I am not jealous!

27
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,360
Who would be jealous of you?

28
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,360
I'm not.

29
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:20,199
Aren't you jealous?

30
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,160
Do you even believe that yourself?

31
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,160
I'm not!

32
00:06:28,312 --> 00:06:29,312
Xiao Meng.

33
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,480
You look so beautiful today.

34
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,800
Auntie.

35
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,398
Do we look like a good match?

36
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,399
Perfect match.

37
00:06:38,439 --> 00:06:39,439
See?

38
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:40,679
That's what everyone says.

39
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,680
Get in.

40
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,120
Get on.

41
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,279
No.

42
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,800
Get on.

43
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,919
Otherwise, I'll shout...

44
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:55,920
"Yang Meng, I love you!"

45
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,439
So the whole village will know.

46
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,240
Yang Meng, I love you!

47
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,560
Yang Meng, I...

48
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:52,839
I'm sorry.

49
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:58,439
Today...

50
00:07:58,879 --> 00:07:59,879
I went too far.

51
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,520
I shouldn't have joked about my own safety.

52
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,600
But...

53
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,040
Why didn't you ask me why?

54
00:08:10,713 --> 00:08:12,033
I was in a bad mood this morning.

55
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:13,839
It was my own problem.

56
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:20,759
It's fine.

57
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:21,920
Next time, Brother Meng...

58
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:23,359
Just remember to make me breakfast.

59
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,279
I want oyster omelettes.

60
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,240
What "Brother Meng"?

61
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,240
Don't you like it when others

62
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,319
call you that?

63
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,200
So I'm the only one who can't?

64
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,799
Don't talk nonsense.

65
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,480
Oh, right!

66
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,600
I found something in your closet today...

67
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,279
Promise me.

68
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,079
No matter what happens in the future,

69
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,280
no matter how important it is,

70
00:08:49,799 --> 00:08:50,360
you must never

71
00:08:50,361 --> 00:08:51,440
joke about your own life.

72
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,720
Don't worry.

73
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,240
I value my life very much.

74
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,200
What exactly is your
relationship with Yang Meng?

75
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:10,960
In what capacity

76
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,000
are you asking me?

77
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:14,000
I'm just reminding you.

78
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,880
Try to be a little more discreet, okay?

79
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,480
It's none of your concern.

80
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:20,080
If anything, you

81
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,840
overreacted,

82
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,519
a bit too much.

83
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,519
Yeah.

84
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,120
What right do I have?

85
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:49,839
Still not asleep this late?

86
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,440
What are you working on?

87
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:52,360
You came at the right time.

88
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,600
Come. Sit.

89
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,000
Look.

90
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,120
Along the main road into the village,

91
00:09:59,399 --> 00:10:00,679
If we set up two bus stops here,

92
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,399
tourist flow would be better managed.

93
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:04,679
And this bracelet,

94
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:07,278
My hope is that in the future,
every person who comes to our village

95
00:10:07,279 --> 00:10:08,279
as a tourist,

96
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,840
could have a bracelet like this.

97
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,080
That way, no matter how much time passes,

98
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,520
whenever they see this bracelet,

99
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:15,119
they'll think of our Lanwan Village.

100
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,360
For them,

101
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,879
it'll be a wonderful memory.

102
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,440
It's very pretty.

103
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:28,000
You are the very first person

104
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,120
to wear this bracelet.

105
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,039
I made it myself.

106
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,360
Don't break it.

107
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:36,679
Are you... helping me?

108
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:39,159
Not really.

109
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,919
I genuinely think

110
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,000
our village is really nice.

111
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:44,000
Every sea breeze here,

112
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:46,080
every tide, I feel...

113
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:49,079
this place truly deserves
to be discovered by more people.

114
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,080
Count me in.

115
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,120
I'll work with you.

116
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,480
Your handwriting is so ugly.

117
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:01,279
Look.

118
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:03,440
This is the old route.

119
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,680
It's already been adjusted.

120
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,440
Really?

121
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,360
Then let me revise it properly.

122
00:11:11,679 --> 00:11:13,519
Why don't you stay with me?

123
00:11:14,279 --> 00:11:15,599
I'm afraid I'll mess it up again.

124
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:19,840
Look here.

125
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,976
The scenery at Little Wild Lake is actually

126
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,639
exceptionally, breathtakingly beautiful.

127
00:11:23,879 --> 00:11:25,120
But hardly anyone goes there.

128
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,480
So here, we could

129
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,759
add one more stop.

130
00:11:27,879 --> 00:11:29,200
But we could move the Lanwan stop

131
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,360
over to this side.

132
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:31,639
Right?

133
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,159
That way, more people would go.

134
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:36,519
And from this location,

135
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,976
around the Fishermen's Tribe area,

136
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,080
if you look at the drawing,

137
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,720
we could actually

138
00:11:41,279 --> 00:11:43,159
add a bit more here.

139
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:44,759
Don't you think?

140
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:55,120
Ungrateful son!

141
00:14:55,639 --> 00:14:56,639
Dad...

142
00:15:30,639 --> 00:15:32,559
A true man stands tall
between heaven and earth!

143
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:33,919
You're a man.

144
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,760
You must do what a man is supposed to do.

145
00:15:35,879 --> 00:15:37,279
You have your own responsibilities.

146
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:54,840
Yoki.

147
00:15:55,639 --> 00:15:56,720
Can you understand me?

148
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,480
What are you doing here?

149
00:16:35,879 --> 00:16:36,879
What's wrong with you?

150
00:16:40,752 --> 00:16:42,152
You've been sitting here all night.

151
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,720
Aren't you cold?

152
00:16:47,679 --> 00:16:48,679
When are you leaving?

153
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:52,840
What do you mean?

154
00:16:54,159 --> 00:16:55,159
Are you kicking me out?

155
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,600
It's fine if you don't leave.

156
00:16:58,559 --> 00:16:59,559
I'll be leaving anyway.

157
00:17:00,559 --> 00:17:01,559
Leaving?

158
00:17:01,679 --> 00:17:02,679
Where are you going?

159
00:17:03,679 --> 00:17:05,095
- Yang Meng...
- It's none of your business.

160
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,119
Yang Meng...

161
00:17:07,519 --> 00:17:08,599
Are you even human?

162
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:09,880
Who did I
stay up all night for?

163
00:17:10,799 --> 00:17:11,799
For me?

164
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:16,599
What is wrong with you?

165
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:20,599
Brother Yang Meng.

166
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:32,240
Are you two...?

167
00:17:38,279 --> 00:17:39,279
Yang Meng.

168
00:17:39,559 --> 00:17:40,559
Yang Meng.

169
00:17:41,079 --> 00:17:42,079
Yang Meng.

170
00:17:48,279 --> 00:17:48,960
I came... I came to bring you

171
00:17:49,039 --> 00:17:50,160
some tomatoes.

172
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:09,359
Yoki.

173
00:19:10,519 --> 00:19:11,519
I'm sorry.

174
00:19:24,519 --> 00:19:25,519
Yang Meng.

175
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,240
What's wrong?

176
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,440
Yang Meng.

177
00:19:35,319 --> 00:19:36,319
What's the issue with us?

178
00:19:41,119 --> 00:19:42,239
There is nothing between us.

179
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,160
Come back!

180
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,440
Yang Meng!

181
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,240
What's the matter with you?

182
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,200
Get back here!

183
00:19:55,519 --> 00:19:56,519
Yang Meng!

184
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:00,960
Yang Meng!

185
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,440
Let me tell you—...

186
00:20:15,559 --> 00:20:16,559
mind your own business.

187
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,440
He is rejecting you.

188
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,279
Do you not understand plain language?

189
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,480
Do you understand plain language?

190
00:20:25,119 --> 00:20:26,119
Are you done?

191
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,480
How amusing.

192
00:20:43,519 --> 00:20:45,055
Not enough fun in your
fancy celebrity circle?

193
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:46,159
So you come here to mess with us?

194
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,160
Huh?

195
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:55,400
Can't stop hitting me, can you?

196
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:58,240
I didn't make all those
action movies for nothing.

197
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,200
And what kind of saint are you?

198
00:21:01,039 --> 00:21:02,439
Stringing Ye Ran along on one hand,

199
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:04,120
and seducing Yang Meng on the other.

200
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:05,640
Yang Meng...?

201
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,840
Stop playing innocent with me!

202
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:11,200
You big idiot!

203
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:13,000
It's Ye Ran that I like!

204
00:21:22,119 --> 00:21:23,000
Next time you decide to hit someone

205
00:21:23,079 --> 00:21:24,319
could you use your brain first?

206
00:21:26,519 --> 00:21:27,880
I should be asking you that.

207
00:21:32,759 --> 00:21:33,759
You really like Ye Ran?

208
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:34,960
What's it to you?

209
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:39,640
So...

210
00:21:40,799 --> 00:21:41,680
You intentionally made me

211
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:43,000
misunderstand you and Yang Meng.

212
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:45,640
I admit it.

213
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:47,240
I used a little trick.

214
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:49,359
But it was to protect Yang Meng.

215
00:21:51,175 --> 00:21:51,774
I can't let my

216
00:21:51,799 --> 00:21:53,119
best friend get hurt.

217
00:21:54,359 --> 00:21:55,599
Especially by someone like you.

218
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:01,200
Come on.

219
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,720
Then tell me,

220
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,240
what kind of person am I?

221
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:08,520
The kind who dates a girl
and gets exposed as a cheating scumbag.

222
00:22:09,279 --> 00:22:10,839
And now comes here to bother Yang Meng.

223
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:13,040
Who knows what your real intentions are?

224
00:22:14,039 --> 00:22:15,359
What are my intentions?

225
00:22:16,119 --> 00:22:17,200
Do I need to tell you?

226
00:22:18,599 --> 00:22:19,599
Then you tell me,

227
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:21,760
what exactly are your
feelings for Yang Meng?

228
00:22:26,279 --> 00:22:27,920
Falling asleep next to him the first time

229
00:22:28,599 --> 00:22:29,599
was an accident.

230
00:22:32,359 --> 00:22:33,359
No nightmares.

231
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:35,560
No waking up in the middle of the night.

232
00:22:36,039 --> 00:22:38,160
After that, I found all sorts of excuses

233
00:22:38,519 --> 00:22:39,519
to stick by his side.

234
00:22:45,319 --> 00:22:46,319
I like Yang Meng.

235
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:49,680
Quite honest.

236
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:54,160
Then let's cooperate.

237
00:22:56,759 --> 00:22:57,759
Cooperate?

238
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:58,920
Yes.

239
00:22:59,359 --> 00:23:00,359
We each get what we want.

240
00:23:03,759 --> 00:23:05,400
We each get what we want?

241
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,160
Buddy,

242
00:23:12,599 --> 00:23:13,920
I never would have thought

243
00:23:15,799 --> 00:23:17,119
you're such a pervert.
